<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - BMC Software restarted.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - BMC Software restarted.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Furman Selz said analyst Sanjiv Hingorani reinitiated BMC Software Inc with a buy rating.</p>
<p>-- sees earnings per share growth at a compounded annual rate of 22.6 percent between fiscal 1996 and 1998.</p>
<p>-- set 12-month price target of $81. Shares rose one to 68-1/4.</p>
</text>
